Source: distiller-genesis
Section: metapackages
Priority: optional
Maintainer: PamirAI Incorporated <founders@pamir.ai>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0
Homepage: https://github.com/pamir-ai-pkgs/distiller-genesis
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/pamir-ai-pkgs/distiller-genesis.git
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/pamir-ai-pkgs/distiller-genesis
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: distiller-genesis-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: distiller-sdk (>= 3.0.0),
            distiller-services (>= 3.0.0),
            distiller-update (>= 3.0.0),
            distiller-telemetry (>= 4.0.0),
            distiller-cc (>= 4.0.0),
            claude-code-web-manager,
            pamir-ai-sam-dkms,
            distiller-platform-update
Suggests: distiller-test-harness (>= 1.0.0)
Description: Common meta-package for Distiller platform
 This meta-package provides the base Distiller software stack that works
 across all supported hardware platforms (Raspberry Pi CM5, Radxa Zero 3/3W,
 ArmSom CM5 IO).
 .
 Includes: SDK, system services, management tools, and universal hardware
 drivers (SAM controller).
 .
 For a complete platform installation, install the appropriate platform-specific
 meta-package: distiller-genesis-cm5 or distiller-genesis-rockchip.

Package: distiller-genesis-cm5
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: distiller-genesis-common (= ${binary:Version}),
            pamir-ai-soundcard-dkms
Description: Complete Distiller stack for Raspberry Pi CM5
 Platform-specific meta-package for Raspberry Pi Compute Module 5 (BCM2712).
 .
 Depends on distiller-genesis-common and adds CM5-specific hardware drivers:
  - pamir-ai-soundcard-dkms: TLV320AIC3204 audio codec (CM5 only)
 .
 This package provides a complete Distiller installation for Raspberry Pi CM5
 hardware.

Package: distiller-genesis-rockchip
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: distiller-genesis-common (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Complete Distiller stack for Rockchip platforms
 Platform-specific meta-package for Rockchip-based devices:
  - Radxa Zero 3/3W (RK3566)
  - ArmSom CM5 IO (RK3576)
 .
 Depends on distiller-genesis-common which includes all necessary drivers
 and services for Rockchip platforms.
 .
 This package provides a complete Distiller installation for Rockchip-based
 hardware.
